title: Sierra Kusterbeck from Neaux and Versa Emerge
itunes:title: Sierra Kusterbeck from Neaux and Versa Emerge
description:
Episode 272 - Happy Wednesday! This week we have an engaging conversation on the rise, fall and rise story with Sierra Kusterbeck from Neaux and Versa Emerge. She rose to prominence as the singer of pop/rock band Versa Emerge in the early 2000’s at an early age, but ran into a wall and has now taken a more nuanced view of creativity and playing music in her band Neaux. It’s a really eye-opening episode that I hope you dive deep into! Pre-order the Neaux record called “Chain Up The Sun” from our buds at The Native Sound!Visit our friends over at No Echo for great features on punk, hardcore and all things heavy.
